{"tid":2253482,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"眾安銀行推自訂號碼卡 享Deliveroo消費回贈","createTime":"2020-10-22T07:38:01.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T07:43:43.000Z","uid":364053,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"4dc7c2f2dc4f05dfca37e3c028b1b2ca6a216413","tid":2253482,"uid":364053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:38:01.000Z","msg":"該行話，由尋日起至2021年1月31日，客戶用「ZA Card」喺特選商戶外賣平台Deliveroo訂餐，就可以獲取11%現金回贈，此外客戶進行網上簽帳都可獲得6%現金回贈，比較埋Mox Bank及WeLab Bank張扣帳卡，兩者現時嘅回贈水平介乎1%至8%，所以ZA Bank回贈幅度都未算低。但要留意嘅係，有別於其他虛銀，其將以ZA Coin形式發放有關回贈，用戶須將帳戶連結至ZA Coin先可以參與上述獎賞活動！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20201020/s00004/1603130871832/眾安銀行推自訂號碼卡-享deliveroo消費回贈\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00004%2F1603130871832%2F%E7%9C%BE%E5%AE%89%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%87%AA%E8%A8%82%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%8D%A1-%E4%BA%ABdeliveroo%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E5%9B%9E%E8%B4%88&d=mhl3ai6H9Odyk596tiaOPStC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=e86d2f38\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2F%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%2Farticle%2F20201020%2Fs00004%2F1603130871832%2F%E7%9C%BE%E5%AE%89%E9%8A%80%E8%A1%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%87%AA%E8%A8%82%E8%99%9F%E7%A2%BC%E5%8D%A1-%E4%BA%ABdeliveroo%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E5%9B%9E%E8%B4%88&h=6e133769\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/pns/經濟/article/20201020/s00004/1603130871832/眾安銀行推自訂號碼卡-享deliveroo消費回贈</a>"},{"pid":"d25f9ea4db7cccf95b31347376da4ff7937d30d7","tid":2253482,"uid":180251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-22T07:43:43.000Z","msg":"點解唔自煮燃發"}]}